 Social protection on ‘‘family/children function’’ as % of GDP: Source Eurostat (European system of integrated social protection statistics ESSPROS database: http:// epp.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/portal/page/portal/ social_protection/introduction), computed as an average of a ten-year period corresponding to the period the respondent was at the reference age. 
