 Maternity leave replacement rate: Maternity/parental leave beneﬁts expressed as a percentage of women’s wages in manufacturing Source SHARELIFE welfare state context variables (http://share-dev.mpisoc. mpg.de/index.php?id=162), computed as an average of a ten year period corresponding to the period when the respondent was at the reference age. 
